commitResults.messageTitle: Add assertions to Parser and TaskList
commitResults.messageBody:
Parser and TaskList classes have no checks that their references to FileManager and Ui instances are properly assigned.

This can lead to a possible NullPointerException in the future if the way the references are set changes.

Add assertions that references are not null before calling them in methods.

commitResults.messageTitle: Improve code quality of Parser and other classes
commitResults.messageBody:
Parser has some nested logic, and unclear boolean flags and method names.

Results in longer methods having bad readability.

* Add clear names to boolean flags
* Add guard clauses
* Rename method names to make more sense
* Correct some coding standard violations and make naming more consistent in other classes
